  <summary date="2018-02-21T22:15:53Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Justice Safety Valve Act of 2017

This bill amends the federal criminal code to authorize a court to impose a sentence below the mandatory minimum if it determines, after considering certain factors, that the mandatory minimum sentence is greater than necessary.</summary>
